parameters: \F[sirius_trouble]Akane: "What the! Where is this...!?"

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[king_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "This is my private room. It's a sacred place within
the 'kingdom' that no one has ever been allowed to enter."

\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[king_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "Even if you bring me to a place like this, I won't
change my heart."

\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[king_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "I want you to see all of me honestly. Above all...
I desire to be loved by you with everything I have."

\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[king_angry]\AA[2]Yurika: "This room is myself. It's orderly and
uninteresting. Being perfect is its only merit. I find peace
here, yet at the same time, I loathe it."

\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[king_angry]\AA[2]Yurika: "My power... my ugliness... I want to lay it all
bare like this."

\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[king_angry]\AA[1]Akane: "What's the point of that!? There's no way I'd push
away someone I love just to be with the president!"
\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[king_angry]\AA[2]Yurika: "...Am I inferior to Shiratora Nadeshiko?"
\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[king_angry]\AA[1]Akane: "!!"

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[king_angry]\AA[2]Yurika: "Then... I shall become Nadeshiko. Just like the
girl you desire. Hairstyle, clothes... even the way I
interact with you, everything..."

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[king_angry]\AA[1]Akane: "Nadeshiko is Nadeshiko! The president is the
president...!"

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[king_angry]\AA[2]Yurika: "To deviate from one's true self... You taught me
the beauty of that! You're here, so it's just that simple!"

\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[king_angry]\AA[1]Akane: "Just that simple...? Someone like the president who
thinks that way will never understand, not in a lifetime!"
\F[sirius_damage]Akane: "Guh...! So strong..!!"

\F[sirius_damage]\FF[king_angry]\AA[2]Yurika: "Is Nadeshiko really necessary here? In the world
for just you and me... inviting her... was that the only
option...?"

\F[sirius_damage]\FF[king_angry]\AA[2]Yurika: "If it's Nadeshiko's persuasion... you would accept
it, right?"
\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[king_angry]\AA[1]Akane: "You still intend to drag Nadeshiko into this!?"

\FF[king_angry]Yurika: "It can't be helped. To open your heart, we must
welcome her into the 'kingdom', to be my right hand..."
\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[king_angry]\AA[1]Akane: (More! If I can get closer...!)
\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[king_angry]\AA[2]Yurika: "I won't let you do that, Akane!"
\F[sirius_damage]\FF[king_angry]\AA[1]Akane: "What!? "

\FF[king_smile]Yurika: "This room is myself. That's why I can freely change
the interior. I can even fix it in place!"
\F[sirius_damage]\FF[king_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "Damn it!! Stop...!"

\F[sirius_damage]\FF[king_ero]\AA[2]Yurika: "You should witness Nadeshiko understanding my
thoughts and obeying. And you too..."

\FF[king_smile]Yurika: "Welcome to my world, Shiratora..."
\FF[king_trouble]Yurika: "Wha...!?"

歩行撫子
\F[nakosu_silhouette]Nadeshiko: "Tag, you're it!"
\F[nakosu_smile]Nadeshiko: "President!!"
\F[nakosu_smile]\FF[king_trouble]\AA[2]Yurika: "What... did you say...!?"
\F[sirius_angry]\FF[king_trouble]\AA[1]Akane: "Nadeshiko! That look...!!"
\F[nakosu_angry]Nadeshiko: "Poison... Burst!!"
倒れキャラ
倒れキャラ
\FF[nakosu_smile]Nadeshiko: "Did I make it in time...? Akane"
\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[nakosu_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "Agent Suits! Why is Nadeshiko... How come!? "

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[nakosu_smile]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "Professor Anjiri said that no matter what, she
couldn't reach the president's location... She's also on
Akane's side, right?"
\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[nakosu_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "Akelunar!? Ah... no..."

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[nakosu_smile]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "It's okay, I heard everything. You don't have to
hide it anymore. Agent Sirius"

\F[sirius_smile]\FF[nakosu_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "Somehow... being called that... It's
embarrassing..."

\F[sirius_smile]\FF[nakosu_smile]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "I thought... if the president was going to
persuade Akane, she would surely call for me."
\F[sirius_smile]\FF[nakosu_smile]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "After all, I know Akane best."

\F[sirius_smile]\FF[nakosu_smile]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "And I said... surely the president would be off
guard. Thinking she could handle me, a mere frail student."

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[nakosu_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "Nadeshiko... Did you decide to wear that suit
yourself!?"

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[nakosu_smile]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "Because if I didn't... I wouldn't be able to
save you, Akane!"
\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[nakosu_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "To think I'd be saved by Nadeshiko..."

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[nakosu_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "(Again... I couldn't be of any help to Nadeshiko...
I'm always the one being saved...)"
\FF[nakosu_angry]Nadeshiko: "Akane! This is...!!"
歩行キングダム
歩行キングダム
\FF[king_trouble]Yurika: "Ah...!! What is happening...!"

\FF[king_trouble]Yurika: "My power is fading away... The 'Kingdom' is
crumbling!"
\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[king_trouble]\AA[1]Akane: "It's over. Your desires end here..."

\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[king_trouble]\AA[1]Akane: "You're going to lose to Nadeshiko and it's over. You
understand what that means, don't you?"

\FF[king_trouble]Yurika: "Lost...? To this girl... I see... She's your
beloved, after all..."

\FF[king_trouble]Yurika: "There's no way I couldn't defeat her. And yet... I
was careless..."

\FF[king_trouble]Yurika: "I'm not perfect. I was just sitting in a world
centered around myself..."
\FF[king_trouble]Yurika: "...I was just a naked emperor, wasn't I?"
